2
00:00:27,000 --> 00:00:31,200
♫  Tearing up all the memories of the past  ♫

3
00:00:31,200 --> 00:00:33,756
♫  Leaving no regrets behind to haunt us  ♫

4
00:00:33,756 --> 00:00:40,736
♫  Exchanging a whole lifetime, just to go back again  ♫

5
00:00:40,736 --> 00:00:44,732
♫  If I decide to let my guard down  ♫

6
00:00:44,732 --> 00:00:49,980
♫  Will I give my heart to the wrong one?  ♫

7
00:00:49,980 --> 00:00:54,524
♫  Daring to give, not fearing destruction  ♫

8
00:00:54,524 --> 00:00:56,832
♫  Love is unwilling to lay dormant  ♫

9
00:00:56,832 --> 00:00:59,872
♫  Unafraid of shaking Heaven and Earth  ♫

10
00:00:59,872 --> 00:01:01,900
♫  Even though we're on different paths  ♫

11
00:01:01,900 --> 00:01:06,400
♫  I have no complaints and no regrets  ♫

12
00:01:06,400 --> 00:01:11,500
♫  Because you are the unsolvable riddle set by fate  ♫

13
00:01:11,500 --> 00:01:15,500
♫  So I pray for a miracle  ♫

14
00:01:15,500 --> 00:01:21,800
♫  The stars turn, even if consumed by time, I only hope to search for you  ♫

15
00:01:21,800 --> 00:01:25,200
♫  Searching for that miracle called forever  ♫

16
00:01:25,200 --> 00:01:30,500
♫  Until death, we'll walk all the way together  ♫

17
00:01:30,500 --> 00:01:38,400
♫  Love is the most beautiful meaning in life  ♫

18
00:01:50,900 --> 00:01:56,200
   

19
00:01:58,023 --> 00:02:02,727
 Legend has it that Lord Ming is the ancient behemoth Kun. 

20
00:02:02,727 --> 00:02:06,487
 It roams the world above the clouds, 

21
00:02:06,487 --> 00:02:10,311
 possessing the power to destroy the world. 
   

22
00:02:10,311 --> 00:02:15,606
 The human sect, Qiyuan Sect, reveres Lord Ming and brings calamity to humanity. 

23
00:02:15,606 --> 00:02:20,386
 The major sects led by Luo Mansion searched everywhere for Lord Ming, 

24
00:02:20,386 --> 00:02:23,200
 wishing to vanquish it. 

25
00:02:23,200 --> 00:02:27,800
 Lord Ming, having absorbed a vast amount of dark energy, is about to lose control. 

26
00:02:27,800 --> 00:02:31,800
 Many civilians who believed in the Qiyuan Sect were turned into stone. 

27
00:02:31,800 --> 00:02:35,000
 A great catastrophe is imminent upon the world. 

28
00:02:38,300 --> 00:02:41,600
   

29
00:02:41,600 --> 00:02:43,800
It's almost time.

30
00:02:43,800 --> 00:02:46,900
Xiao Huan, seal away Qi's memories

31
00:02:46,900 --> 00:02:49,300
and send her to the Mortal Realm.

32
00:02:51,827 --> 00:02:57,746
The hope of saving all beings in the future is now on her.

33
00:03:58,187 --> 00:04:00,987
Master, I know it's you.

34
00:04:03,547 --> 00:04:06,947
Master, stop hiding. Hurry, come out.

35
00:04:15,266 --> 00:04:18,507
Has Commander Ying agreed to take us to the human world?

36
00:04:23,186 --> 00:04:27,346
Master, what's wrong with you? You're acting strange today.

37
00:04:30,826 --> 00:04:34,166
Qi, your thought sword originates from thoughts.

38
00:04:34,166 --> 00:04:36,806
Do you know your mission behind that sword?

39
00:04:38,986 --> 00:04:41,287
My mission behind the sword?

40
00:04:41,287 --> 00:04:44,886
Does carrying a sword mean I must kill people?

41
00:04:44,886 --> 00:04:47,427
But I don't want to kill anyone.

42
00:04:51,626 --> 00:04:54,466
Master, what do you want to do?

43
00:05:02,307 --> 00:05:06,266
Master, what are you going to do?

44
00:05:10,800 --> 00:05:15,700
   

45
00:05:16,800 --> 00:05:19,500
 Master, I know it's you. 

46
00:05:19,500 --> 00:05:22,900
 Master, stop hiding. Hurry, come out. 

47
00:05:22,900 --> 00:05:24,400
 Qi... 

48
00:05:25,200 --> 00:05:26,800
 Qi. 

49
00:05:26,800 --> 00:05:31,400
Qi. Qi, wake up.

50
00:05:37,000 --> 00:05:38,700
Awake?

51
00:05:41,026 --> 00:05:44,386
Yue... Jin...

52
00:05:45,500 --> 00:05:48,200
zhao!

53
00:05:49,186 --> 00:05:51,692
What are you doing? Why did you pinch me?

54
00:05:51,692 --> 00:05:53,106
   

55
00:05:53,106 --> 00:05:54,787
I dreamed of my master again.

56
00:05:54,787 --> 00:05:58,447
If you hadn't suddenly interrupted, I would've clearly seen what he looked like.

57
00:05:58,447 --> 00:06:02,106
Enough. You say this every time. If you could see him, you would have a while ago.

58
00:06:02,106 --> 00:06:05,100
I'm guessing your master doesn't exist at all.

59
00:06:05,100 --> 00:06:07,100
Who says he doesn't exist?

60
00:06:07,100 --> 00:06:11,400
If he doesn't exist, where did I learn those moves from?

61
00:06:13,906 --> 00:06:18,506
Yue Qi, I worked really hard to take care of you for three years,

62
00:06:18,506 --> 00:06:22,128
but I can't hold a candle to your faceless master. 
    

63
00:06:28,466 --> 00:06:31,387
Talk nicely. Don't use violence.

64
00:06:32,146 --> 00:06:34,186
I must use violence, I will!

65
00:06:34,186 --> 00:06:35,586
I will!

66
00:06:35,586 --> 00:06:37,387
I'm going to smack you.

67
00:06:37,387 --> 00:06:39,726
I'm your elder brother!

68
00:06:41,987 --> 00:06:43,507
Who says you're older than me?

69
00:06:43,507 --> 00:06:45,947
Three years ago, when we woke up in Wuyan Village,

70
00:06:45,947 --> 00:06:48,466
neither of us remembered what happened before.

71
00:06:48,466 --> 00:06:52,746
Also, it was you who said that our birthdays were on the same day.

72
00:06:54,267 --> 00:06:59,206
You don't understand anything else, but you remember this clearly.

73
00:07:00,146 --> 00:07:03,626
Well, today is the 14th day of the 7th month, our birthday.

74
00:07:03,626 --> 00:07:05,547
So, what should we eat?

75
00:07:05,547 --> 00:07:06,706
Egg noodles?

76
00:07:06,706 --> 00:07:08,126
Let's go!

77
00:07:09,787 --> 00:07:11,787
Here, enjoy your meal.

78
00:07:15,146 --> 00:07:17,507
- A bowl of egg noodles, please. 
 - Without green onions.

79
00:07:17,507 --> 00:07:18,987
Okay!

80
00:07:21,800 --> 00:07:25,800
Qi, your hair rope is so worn out. Let's replace it.

81
00:07:25,800 --> 00:07:27,100
I can't throw it away.

82
00:07:27,100 --> 00:07:29,000
I was wearing it when I woke up.

83
00:07:29,000 --> 00:07:31,200
It might be related to my background.

84
00:07:31,200 --> 00:07:33,400
Maybe my master gave it to me.

85
00:07:33,400 --> 00:07:35,300
I really do hope you have a master.

86
00:07:35,300 --> 00:07:37,600
That way, we would have a clue about our origins.

87
00:07:37,600 --> 00:07:40,200
I really did dream of him.

88
00:07:40,200 --> 00:07:44,900
It's just that, in my dream, I couldn't see his face.

89
00:07:44,900 --> 00:07:48,100
Nor remember what he said.

90
00:07:48,100 --> 00:07:51,700
But I was thinking...

91
00:07:51,700 --> 00:07:53,000
- thinking... 
 - Your noodles are here.

92
00:07:53,000 --> 00:07:54,600
Thinking what?

93
00:07:56,787 --> 00:07:57,967
Enjoy.

94
00:07:57,967 --> 00:08:00,100
I must be hungry!

95
00:08:00,100 --> 00:08:02,000
What are you doing?

96
00:08:03,700 --> 00:08:06,600
Jinzhao, you said you were older than me.

97
00:08:06,600 --> 00:08:08,800
Show me some love.

98
00:08:08,800 --> 00:08:12,000
The same old rules. Whoever grabs it get to eat it.

99
00:08:50,706 --> 00:08:54,107
You said it. Whoever grabs it first gets it.

100
00:08:54,107 --> 00:08:56,327
You eat it.

101
00:08:58,387 --> 00:09:00,327
Why aren't you eating?

102
00:09:01,267 --> 00:09:03,626
Yue Jinzhao, are you serious?

103
00:09:03,626 --> 00:09:07,987
Do you have to use Mindlink to snatch an egg?

104
00:09:28,920 --> 00:09:30,688
   

105
00:09:31,787 --> 00:09:33,687
You're cheating. You learned to be bad!

106
00:09:33,687 --> 00:09:36,666
I learned that from you!

107
00:09:38,586 --> 00:09:41,026
This bowl of noodles is mine now.

108
00:09:46,987 --> 00:09:49,687
Why do you love egg noodles so much?

109
00:09:51,466 --> 00:09:55,766
Because it is the first food you ever made for me.

110
00:09:58,600 --> 00:10:04,400
Qi, eat slower. Leave some soup for me.

111
00:10:10,700 --> 00:10:12,300
Time to work.

112
00:10:15,300 --> 00:10:16,600
I drew this last night.

113
00:10:16,600 --> 00:10:19,400
This is the person I saw with my left eye.

114
00:10:19,400 --> 00:10:21,000
Wow, are these scribbles?

115
00:10:21,000 --> 00:10:23,400
What? What scribbles?

116
00:10:23,400 --> 00:10:26,300
This captures both the person's spirit and looks. Okay?

117
00:10:27,300 --> 00:10:29,400
It can ward off evil.

118
00:10:32,107 --> 00:10:33,747
Stop joking around.

119
00:10:33,747 --> 00:10:36,667
Compared to your dream, my left eye is more reliable.

120
00:10:36,667 --> 00:10:38,304
Every time the trail goes cold,

121
00:10:38,304 --> 00:10:41,946
my left eye always manages to foresee something, although...

122
00:10:41,946 --> 00:10:46,007
Although the price of seeing the future is intense pain in your left eye.

123
00:10:46,007 --> 00:10:49,347
I can recite these words of yours by heart now.

124
00:10:49,347 --> 00:10:51,486
Why do you care?

125
00:10:51,486 --> 00:10:54,700
Anyway, this time in Yinghui Fort, we have to find this man in red.

126
00:10:54,700 --> 00:10:58,240
No matter what, we must find him.

127
00:10:58,900 --> 00:11:01,400
   

128
00:11:20,307 --> 00:11:24,906
Jinzhao, you haven't given me this year's birthday present yet.

129
00:11:27,400 --> 00:11:29,500
It's all yours. Buy whatever.

130
00:11:29,500 --> 00:11:32,200
Why are you so generous today?

131
00:11:38,700 --> 00:11:42,400
Yue Jinzhao, you don't plan to give me a birthday present, is that it?

132
00:11:42,400 --> 00:11:44,400
No, I'm out of money.

133
00:11:44,400 --> 00:11:46,800
If we keep going like this, we'll go bankrupt.

134
00:11:46,800 --> 00:11:50,400
Think about it. Inn costs aside, last night we had two large bowls of beef noodles.

135
00:11:50,400 --> 00:11:51,800
That was eight coins.

136
00:11:51,800 --> 00:11:54,800
You're a glutton, so we spent another five coins.

137
00:11:54,800 --> 00:11:57,100
In the end, you even took a chestnut cake.

138
00:11:57,100 --> 00:12:01,200
Most importantly, you were still hungry and ate another two bowls of egg noodles!

139
00:12:01,200 --> 00:12:03,500
We're out of money.

140
00:12:05,200 --> 00:12:07,600
So, we must find this person first.

141
00:12:07,600 --> 00:12:08,700
I've calculated it.

142
00:12:08,700 --> 00:12:13,400
With our pace, within two hours, we can run through the entire Yinghui Fort.

143
00:12:14,500 --> 00:12:17,400
Although it's a foolish method.

144
00:12:17,400 --> 00:12:19,700
Then you come up with a smart way.

145
00:12:20,706 --> 00:12:22,246
Let's go.

146
00:12:24,000 --> 00:12:26,900
Start from this point and meet here in two hours.

147
00:12:26,900 --> 00:12:29,200
Got it, Smelly Jinzhao.

148
00:12:32,300 --> 00:12:36,500
Have a look. Top-notch jewelry. Miss.

149
00:12:36,500 --> 00:12:41,600
- Sir, how much is this? 
 - 10 coins.

150
00:12:41,600 --> 00:12:43,500
10 coins?

151
00:12:43,500 --> 00:12:46,200
More expensive than two bowls of beef noodles.

152
00:12:57,706 --> 00:13:01,307
That annoying guy didn't give me money. Stupid Jinzhao.

153
00:13:02,500 --> 00:13:05,000
   

154
00:13:05,906 --> 00:13:09,747
Recruiting mourners, 3 meals included,

155
00:13:09,747 --> 00:13:11,630
10 coins a day.

156
00:13:11,630 --> 00:13:14,400
Exactly.

157
00:13:14,400 --> 00:13:15,800
I want to make money.

158
00:13:15,800 --> 00:13:18,100
All right. Just try crying.

159
00:13:18,100 --> 00:13:19,700
Okay.

160
00:13:25,547 --> 00:13:27,987
I can't cry. How do I cry?

161
00:13:28,000 --> 00:13:30,600
Just cry like you did when your family died.

162
00:13:30,600 --> 00:13:31,700
I don't have a family.

163
00:13:31,700 --> 00:13:33,800
You don't have a family. Isn't that very pitiful?

164
00:13:33,800 --> 00:13:35,800
But I've got Jinzhao. I'm not pitiful at all.

165
00:13:35,800 --> 00:13:37,900
That said, after a person dies,

166
00:13:37,900 --> 00:13:40,600
they enter the cycle of reincarnation, which means starting over again.

167
00:13:40,600 --> 00:13:43,000
Why should I cry?

168
00:13:43,000 --> 00:13:45,800
This girl doesn't seem like a normal person.

169
00:13:45,800 --> 00:13:48,800
Miss, you should be on your way.

170
00:13:50,187 --> 00:13:53,146
Oh, no! The horse was spooked!

171
00:14:13,706 --> 00:14:15,347
Are you all right?

172
00:14:17,000 --> 00:14:18,500
Child, are you okay?

173
00:14:18,500 --> 00:14:20,900
    
 Thank you very much. Thank her.

174
00:14:20,900 --> 00:14:22,700
Master, are you okay?

175
00:14:22,700 --> 00:14:26,000
Go check if anyone was injured and check the damage to the shops.

176
00:14:26,000 --> 00:14:27,500
Yes!

177
00:14:35,100 --> 00:14:37,600
Sorry, Miss. That horse belongs to my family.

178
00:14:37,600 --> 00:14:41,500
It got startled just now. Thank you for your help.

179
00:14:41,500 --> 00:14:45,900
Red clothes. High ponytail.

180
00:14:49,586 --> 00:14:51,107
Miss?

181
00:14:59,547 --> 00:15:03,506
But you're much prettier than the picture.

182
00:15:07,627 --> 00:15:10,506
This is a thank-you gift. Please accept it.

183
00:15:11,400 --> 00:15:13,600
Thank you, sir. You're so generous,

184
00:15:13,600 --> 00:15:16,800
but ten coins will be enough for me.

185
00:15:18,200 --> 00:15:20,700
This is what you deserve for your kindness.

186
00:15:20,700 --> 00:15:23,400
I have to go. Goodbye.

187
00:15:32,800 --> 00:15:35,200
There were no white ones left. This green one is okay. Right?

188
00:15:35,200 --> 00:15:37,500
 Great Lord Ming, blessings upon all beings. 

189
00:15:37,500 --> 00:15:41,200
Our sect serves Lord Ming and makes people happy!

190
00:15:41,200 --> 00:15:44,700
Anyone who asks shall receive! Don't you agree?

191
00:15:44,700 --> 00:15:46,100
Anyone shall receive? 
    

192
00:15:46,100 --> 00:15:48,300
 - We tell the masses...  
 - Let me go take a look.

193
00:15:48,300 --> 00:15:51,800
 Can the Qiyuan Sect help me and Jinzhao find our origins? 

194
00:15:51,800 --> 00:15:55,800
 - May Lord Ming bless us! 
 - May Lord Ming bless us! 

195
00:15:55,800 --> 00:16:00,000
Master Meng, why aren't the two people who Lord Shengxuan invited here yet?

196
00:16:00,000 --> 00:16:01,900
What's the rush?

197
00:16:06,000 --> 00:16:09,600
The faith in Lord Ming is very strong!

198
00:16:09,600 --> 00:16:14,200
He is now traveling the world and blessing us all from afar.

199
00:16:14,200 --> 00:16:17,800
We should pay even more homage to Lord Ming!

200
00:16:17,800 --> 00:16:19,600
May Lord Ming bless us!

201
00:16:19,600 --> 00:16:21,900
 - May Lord Ming bless us!  
 - Hasn't one just arrived?

202
00:16:21,900 --> 00:16:23,700
May Lord Ming bless us!

203
00:16:23,700 --> 00:16:26,200
Miss, you don't look familiar.  
  - May Lord Ming bless us! 

204
00:16:26,200 --> 00:16:28,800
Is it your first time hearing about our sect?

205
00:16:28,800 --> 00:16:30,000
Who are you?

206
00:16:30,000 --> 00:16:31,200
    
 I am Meng Cheng.

207
00:16:31,200 --> 00:16:34,000
I'm an emissary of the Qiyuan Sect.

208
00:16:35,200 --> 00:16:38,700
I've forgotten my past. Can you tell me about it?

209
00:16:38,700 --> 00:16:42,300
Your past? That's a piece of cake.

210
00:16:42,300 --> 00:16:46,200
To tell you the truth, I'm proficient in Qiyuan's magic spells.

211
00:16:46,200 --> 00:16:48,600
Magic spells?

212
00:16:48,600 --> 00:16:51,700
Then can you tell me about my origins?

213
00:16:52,506 --> 00:16:54,006
Please wait.

214
00:17:03,867 --> 00:17:06,146
We agreed to meet here.

215
00:17:06,146 --> 00:17:08,466
Where did Qi run off to now?

216
00:17:14,000 --> 00:17:15,900
Qi's over there.

217
00:17:22,200 --> 00:17:23,800
I see it.

218
00:17:23,800 --> 00:17:25,600
You must come from a rich or noble family,

219
00:17:25,600 --> 00:17:29,000
and you snuck out to have fun without your family's knowledge.

220
00:17:32,200 --> 00:17:33,500
You're wrong.

221
00:17:33,500 --> 00:17:37,500
If I were of wealth or nobility, why hasn't my family come looking for me?

222
00:17:37,500 --> 00:17:41,400
Well... haven't you forgotten all about your past?

223
00:17:41,400 --> 00:17:43,100
How do you know I'm wrong then?

224
00:17:43,100 --> 00:17:47,800
Moreover, our Qiyuan's Lord Ming is omniscient towards all matters in the world.

225
00:17:47,800 --> 00:17:50,300
He certainly wouldn't be wrong.

226
00:17:53,000 --> 00:17:56,700
Then tell me, where is my family right now?

227
00:17:56,700 --> 00:17:59,200
Miss, your faith is insufficient.

228
00:17:59,200 --> 00:18:02,500
I can't divine any further for you.

229
00:18:02,500 --> 00:18:04,400
You simply don't know.

230
00:18:04,400 --> 00:18:05,700
Not so.

231
00:18:05,700 --> 00:18:09,000
Insufficient faith means that you don't have enough merit yet.

232
00:18:09,000 --> 00:18:12,700
But today, if you offer a small amount of gold and silver to Lord Ming,

233
00:18:12,700 --> 00:18:15,000
you can increase your connection with him.

234
00:18:15,000 --> 00:18:17,800
Then I'll be able to divine for you.

235
00:18:19,700 --> 00:18:22,900
Look! So many people are accumulating merits.

236
00:18:22,900 --> 00:18:26,600
You should go now, or it'll be too late.

237
00:18:31,200 --> 00:18:35,500
 Believe the Qiyuan Sect and receive Lord Ming's blessing! 

238
00:18:35,500 --> 00:18:38,400
Pay homage to Lord Ming to accumulate merits.

239
00:18:39,046 --> 00:18:41,466
Pay homage to Lord Ming.

240
00:18:42,200 --> 00:18:44,200
Miss, I've been investigating this sect.

241
00:18:44,200 --> 00:18:47,400
The so-called merits are just a means for them to collect money. Don't be fooled.

242
00:18:47,400 --> 00:18:49,800
Nonsense. They bring the people benefits.

243
00:18:49,800 --> 00:18:52,800
- We make these donations voluntarily to Lord Ming. 
 - Yes!

244
00:18:52,800 --> 00:18:54,800
- Exactly. 
 - We do it voluntarily!

245
00:18:54,800 --> 00:18:57,100
- It's voluntary. 
 - Voluntary.

246
00:19:12,600 --> 00:19:14,900
   

247
00:19:16,368 --> 00:19:19,440
   

248
00:19:20,946 --> 00:19:21,747
 Let's set off. 

249
00:19:21,800 --> 00:19:23,000
 All right. 

250
00:19:23,000 --> 00:19:25,600
 It's him. He's the key to finding our origins. 

251
00:19:25,600 --> 00:19:27,100
 We must find a way to gain his trust. 

252
00:19:27,100 --> 00:19:29,200
Your merit is respectable.

253
00:19:32,100 --> 00:19:35,200
This person slanders our sect with malicious intent. Stop him!

254
00:19:35,200 --> 00:19:36,600
- Stop him! 
 - That's right!

255
00:19:36,600 --> 00:19:39,000
How could the Qiyuan Sect be slandered at will?

256
00:19:39,000 --> 00:19:40,400
Who is this?

257
00:19:40,400 --> 00:19:42,200
Jinzhao!

