00:20:01,600 --> 00:20:03,500
   
   

264
00:20:03,500 --> 00:20:05,200
No big deal, no big deal.

265
00:20:05,200 --> 00:20:09,000
This young man really speaks the truth. Well said.

266
00:20:09,000 --> 00:20:13,000
Everything is thanks to Lord Ming's blessing.

267
00:20:13,000 --> 00:20:13,800
That's correct!

268
00:20:13,800 --> 00:20:16,100
- May Lord Ming bless us! 
  - May Lord Ming bless us! 

