00:20:28,500 --> 00:20:30,100
Lord Ming is the chief culprit.

272
00:20:30,100 --> 00:20:33,100
I won't allow anyone to be an accomplice to evil!

273
00:20:34,400 --> 00:20:36,500
You keep insulting the Qiyuan Sect.

274
00:20:36,500 --> 00:20:39,000
You're the one to blame.

275
00:20:39,000 --> 00:20:41,800
Emissary Meng, I'll definitely teach him a good lesson!

276
00:20:41,800 --> 00:20:46,000
Good. May Lord Ming bless you. He'll help you punish this hellion.

277
00:20:46,000 --> 00:20:48,900
Sir, why not join our sect and you can ascend?

278
00:20:48,900 --> 00:20:50,700
Is it a real fight, Jinzhao?

279
00:20:50,700 --> 00:20:53,000
Of course. Let's go!

280
00:21:15,907 --> 00:21:17,626
Jinzhao!

281
00:21:23,244 --> 00:21:26,316
   

282
00:21:49,442 --> 00:21:51,186
- Jinzhao! 
 - This place is dangerous.

283
00:21:51,186 --> 00:21:54,027
- Emissary Meng, please retreat. 
 - A-Alright.

284
00:21:54,027 --> 00:21:55,306
Wait a moment!

285
00:21:55,306 --> 00:21:57,627
You said we should join the sect. Was that true?

286
00:21:57,627 --> 00:21:59,267
I'll wait for you at the Fujin Hall later.

287
00:21:59,267 --> 00:22:02,447
All right, then I'll deal with this madman first.

288
00:22:06,627 --> 00:22:08,407
Hold this.

