00:22:47,166 --> 00:22:49,706
 This girl is so strong. 

291
00:22:49,706 --> 00:22:52,027
Qi, stop.

292
00:22:55,107 --> 00:22:57,586
Buddy, my apologies for offending you just now.

293
00:22:57,586 --> 00:22:58,927
What do you mean?

294
00:22:58,927 --> 00:23:01,867
