298
00:23:12,691 --> 00:23:13,846
You really are naive.

299
00:23:13,846 --> 00:23:16,147
Who says I was deceived?

300
00:23:16,147 --> 00:23:18,666
That bag just now was filled with stones.

301
00:23:18,666 --> 00:23:20,347
Not a single coin in it.

302
00:23:20,347 --> 00:23:22,726
All the coins are here.

303
00:23:22,726 --> 00:23:25,347
Since when did you learn to play tricks on people?

304
00:23:25,347 --> 00:23:28,466
