314
00:23:59,227 --> 00:24:01,147
and is much loved.

315
00:24:01,147 --> 00:24:05,526
I've heard a storyteller say that your family is known as the Twilight Luo Family.

316
00:24:05,526 --> 00:24:10,086
Twins in your family all pass away before reaching their twenties or thirties.

317
00:24:10,086 --> 00:24:13,227
