329
00:24:45,186 --> 00:24:48,786
They've been gone for a while. If we wait any longer, we won't catch them.

330
00:24:50,306 --> 00:24:51,987
Thanks for the help, then.

331
00:24:54,426 --> 00:24:59,226
Qi, he's the one I saw with my left eye.

332
00:25:01,227 --> 00:25:02,727
Watch him.

333
00:25:03,586 --> 00:25:06,766
- Okay, I'll definitely keep a close eye on him. 
 - Let's go.

334
00:25:13,027 --> 00:25:14,767
Miss Yue.

335
00:25:14,767 --> 00:25:16,367
What?

336
00:25:17,506 --> 00:25:20,666
Nothing. Nothing...

337
00:25:21,446 --> 00:25:25,107
Brother Luo Luo, how old are you and where is your home?

338
00:25:25,107 --> 00:25:27,606
How many in your family? Are you married?

339
00:25:27,606 --> 00:25:29,706
She doesn't mean that.

340
00:25:30,987 --> 00:25:33,307
- That's exactly what I mean. 
 - Do you know what you're saying?

341
00:25:33,307 --> 00:25:37,166
Am I not asking for his information?

342
00:25:37,166 --> 00:25:42,766
Brother Yue, I know Miss Yue definitely has no interest in me.

343
00:25:42,766 --> 00:25:46,147
No, no, I am interested in you.

344
00:25:46,147 --> 00:25:50,547
I... I-I-I'm really a boring man.

345
00:25:50,547 --> 00:25:53,586
Brother Luo, he has entered Fujin Hall.

346
00:25:53,586 --> 00:25:57,326
If we want to find out whether this is a stronghold of the Qiyuan Sect or not,

347
00:25:57,326 --> 00:25:59,666
we'll have to go in first.

348
00:26:00,786 --> 00:26:02,867
It seems you have a clever plan.

349
00:26:02,867 --> 00:26:05,147
I just gained that person's trust.

350
00:26:05,147 --> 00:26:07,887
I plan to pretend to join them to see if he can take me inside.

351
00:26:07,887 --> 00:26:11,580
