352
00:26:12,306 --> 00:26:13,966
Here.

353
00:26:17,147 --> 00:26:18,586
What about mine?

354
00:26:18,586 --> 00:26:20,347
Right, what about hers?

355
00:26:21,946 --> 00:26:23,867
It's up to you two.

356
00:26:24,946 --> 00:26:27,306
I'll assist out here. If you two need me, call me.

357
00:26:27,306 --> 00:26:29,546
Of course. Let's go.

358
00:26:39,627 --> 00:26:42,706
You almost drove Luo Zhaoyan away just now. Do you know that?

359
00:26:42,706 --> 00:26:45,227
But that's how it's written in the storybooks.

360
00:26:45,227 --> 00:26:48,867
