363
00:26:57,206 --> 00:26:59,167
His name is Luo Zhaoyan.

364
00:26:59,167 --> 00:27:02,247
You can respectfully address him as Master Luo or call him Brother Luo affectionately

365
00:27:02,247 --> 00:27:05,387
