366
00:27:05,387 --> 00:27:07,826
Because it represents his good manners.

367
00:27:13,907 --> 00:27:18,246
All right. Since you don't like me calling him that, I won't call him that anymore.

368
00:27:18,246 --> 00:27:22,127
If you don't want me to ask questions, then I won't ask again either.

369
00:27:22,127 --> 00:27:24,386
Little flatterer.

370
00:27:29,666 --> 00:27:32,207
