375
00:27:43,627 --> 00:27:48,206
Even though he got something, we still managed to drive him off!

376
00:27:48,206 --> 00:27:50,767
What's that? It's all thanks to Lord Ming's protection.

377
00:27:50,767 --> 00:27:54,746
Emissary Meng, you said earlier you would let us join your sect. Is that true?

378
00:27:54,746 --> 00:27:56,786
Of course, it's true.

379
00:27:56,786 --> 00:27:58,706
You two are truly loyal to Lord Ming.

380
00:27:58,706 --> 00:28:01,247
You will surely receive his grace.

381
00:28:01,247 --> 00:28:04,087
Thank you, Emissary Meng. This is a little token of my appreciation.

382
00:28:04,087 --> 00:28:06,827
Please accept it.

383
00:28:06,827 --> 00:28:09,267
You don't have to.

384
00:28:11,426 --> 00:28:14,706
Qi, you're being naughty again.

385
00:28:15,747 --> 00:28:17,426
Emissary Meng.

386
00:28:19,267 --> 00:28:24,627
Emissary Meng, we sincerely wish to join the sect.

387
00:28:24,627 --> 00:28:28,907
Since you seem to understand, follow me.

388
00:28:42,267 --> 00:28:44,227
 Take care, sir. 

389
00:28:51,786 --> 00:28:54,426
 These flowers look so strange. 

390
00:28:55,627 --> 00:28:57,826
