396
00:29:22,247 --> 00:29:24,507
- So interesting. 
 - Don't touch it!

397
00:29:25,267 --> 00:29:29,227
These were the followers who were fortunate enough to ascend.

398
00:29:29,227 --> 00:29:31,747
These were all real people?

399
00:29:32,907 --> 00:29:37,047
Emissary Meng, this is the ascension as practiced by our sect?

400
00:29:38,747 --> 00:29:42,507
Not just anyone is eligible and fortunate enough to ascend.

401
00:29:42,507 --> 00:29:46,786
Aside from Minister Gao Xiao, even I have to put in extra effort.

402
00:29:46,786 --> 00:29:49,387
Minister? What minister?

403
00:29:49,387 --> 00:29:51,726
You're not aware of this, are you?

404
00:29:51,726 --> 00:29:54,786
Beneath our Lord Ming is Shengxuan.

405
00:29:54,786 --> 00:29:57,347
Shengxuan conveys the lord's command to the sect leader.

406
00:29:57,347 --> 00:29:59,706
The sect leader oversees the ministers of various regions.

407
00:29:59,706 --> 00:30:01,666
Under the ministers are emissaries such as me.

408
00:30:01,666 --> 00:30:06,186
Each emissary is responsible for leading and managing the disciples.

409
00:30:07,466 --> 00:30:14,606
I understand now. So the sect in the Yinghui Fort is governed by Minister Gao Xiao.

410
00:30:14,606 --> 00:30:16,460
That's right.

411
00:30:17,026 --> 00:30:18,466
The laws are strict and clear.

412
00:30:18,466 --> 00:30:20,706
It's worthy of a large sect with followers everywhere!

413
00:30:20,706 --> 00:30:23,267
Qi! We've found ourselves a big backer!

414
00:30:23,267 --> 00:30:27,486
The sect is amazing, and Emissary Meng is also impressive.

415
00:30:27,486 --> 00:30:29,007
Let's go.

