425
00:31:34,867 --> 00:31:39,147
Though the two of you are quite skilled, your brains...

426
00:31:43,767 --> 00:31:47,387
Emissary Meng, we sincerely wish to join your sect.

427
00:31:47,387 --> 00:31:49,206
Why did you lock us up?

428
00:31:49,206 --> 00:31:53,826
