433
00:32:10,887 --> 00:32:12,186
Me too.

434
00:32:12,186 --> 00:32:15,886
But don't worry. We'll get help soon.

435
00:32:24,706 --> 00:32:26,087
Mini—

436
00:32:32,586 --> 00:32:34,367
Minister Gao.

437
00:32:36,907 --> 00:32:38,180
Minister Gao.

