448
00:33:11,267 --> 00:33:13,267
Say that again. What did you just say?

449
00:33:13,267 --> 00:33:15,966
I locked them in the passageway.

450
00:33:15,966 --> 00:33:19,607
Good job! I'll credit you for this.

451
00:33:19,607 --> 00:33:23,087
I'll go report it to Lord Shengxuan.

452
00:33:25,186 --> 00:33:29,586
No need, Gao Xiao. We're here.

453
00:33:34,946 --> 00:33:37,627
Wait! Didn't you say it was two people?

454
00:33:37,627 --> 00:33:39,766
But there are three.

455
00:33:40,846 --> 00:33:42,946
Aren't you that madman?

456
00:33:42,946 --> 00:33:44,227
You!

457
00:33:45,266 --> 00:33:48,407
