459
00:33:50,407 --> 00:33:53,367
Guards! Attack!

460
00:34:44,147 --> 00:34:47,467
I-I-I'll go call for help. I'm going to get help.

461
00:34:52,147 --> 00:34:56,107
You're unlucky to have meet our Qi.

462
00:35:07,986 --> 00:35:10,127
Hero, please spare my life! Spare my life!

463
00:35:10,127 --> 00:35:13,786
