469
00:35:35,836 --> 00:35:39,455
Today, I'm going to wreck this place of yours.

470
00:35:50,726 --> 00:35:52,367
Jinzhao!

471
00:35:53,466 --> 00:35:54,826
Qi!

472
00:35:54,826 --> 00:35:57,967
Jinzhao. Jinzhao!

473
00:35:58,706 --> 00:36:00,506
Miss Yue.

474
00:36:09,087 --> 00:36:10,487
What have you done to Qi?

475
00:36:10,487 --> 00:36:14,526
She... I...

476
00:36:21,007 --> 00:36:23,867
They've merged... They've merged!

477
00:36:23,867 --> 00:36:26,626
Only Lord Ming can merge with the soul fish.

478
00:36:26,626 --> 00:36:28,867
Lord Ming.

479
00:36:28,867 --> 00:36:32,307
Lord Ming has appeared!

480
00:36:33,986 --> 00:36:37,867
 May Lord Ming bless us. 

481
00:36:38,967 --> 00:36:42,106
