482
00:36:42,106 --> 00:36:45,087
so you came out to guide us!

483
00:36:45,087 --> 00:36:49,106
No, I'm not Lord Ming. I'm not!

484
00:36:49,106 --> 00:36:51,387
Jinzhao, think of something!

485
00:36:51,387 --> 00:36:52,946
Qi.

486
00:37:22,387 --> 00:37:24,086
 Jinzhao. 

487
00:37:25,646 --> 00:37:27,406
 Jinzhao. 

488
00:37:29,327 --> 00:37:31,147
 Jinzhao. 

489
00:37:32,387 --> 00:37:33,986
 Jinzhao! 

490
00:37:42,267 --> 00:37:44,907
 Jinzhao. Jinzhao! 

491
00:37:54,907 --> 00:37:56,247
 Qi. 

492
00:37:56,247 --> 00:37:59,347
 Qi, hurry, come back. 

493
00:37:59,347 --> 00:38:00,406
 Come back to me, Qi. 

494
00:38:00,406 --> 00:38:02,746
 - Who are you? 
 - Don't listen to her. 

495
00:38:02,746 --> 00:38:04,007
 Qi, don't listen to her! 

496
00:38:04,007 --> 00:38:06,066
 - Jinzhao. 
 - Don't listen to her. 

497
00:38:06,066 --> 00:38:07,347
 Jinzhao abandoned you. 

498
00:38:07,347 --> 00:38:09,767
 - No! 
 - Jinzhao has abandoned you. 

499
00:38:09,767 --> 00:38:11,406
 - Who are you? 
 - Jinzhao abandoned you. 

500
00:38:11,406 --> 00:38:13,207
 Don't listen to her. 

501
00:38:13,207 --> 00:38:14,826
 I won't deceive you. 

502
00:38:14,826 --> 00:38:16,667
 Qi, quick come back to me! 

503
00:38:16,667 --> 00:38:18,307
 Qi! 

504
00:38:18,307 --> 00:38:20,067
 - Jinzhao abandoned you. 
 - Qi! 

